'''里夫人'''（[[里夫语|里夫语]]：Irifiyen；{{lang-ar|الريفيون}}；{{lang-es|Rifeños}}），[[北非|北非]]民族，[[柏柏尔人|柏柏尔人]]的一支，居住于[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]的[[里夫山脉|里夫山脉]]地区<ref name="Minahan2016p352">{{cite book|author=James B. Minahan|title=Encyclopedia of Stateless Nations: Ethnic and National Groups around the World, 2nd Edition |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pGClDAAAQBAJ |year=2016|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-1-61069-954-9|pages=352}}</ref>。里夫人的传统居住地区接近[[伊比利亚半岛|伊比利亚半岛]]，因此在[[西班牙|西班牙]]南部也有许多里夫人分布<ref>{{citation |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5fUBAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA450|title=The International Handbook on Gender, Migration and Transnationalism|author=Irina Casado i Aijon|publisher=Edward Elgar Publishing|year=2013|isbn=978-1-78195-147-7|editor1=Laura Oso|pages=450 with notes 2-8|editor2=Natalia Ribas-Mateos}}</ref>。在西欧的部分国家如[[法国|法国]]、[[荷兰|荷兰]]等地也有大量移民分布<ref>{{cite book|author1=Malcolm Klein|author2=Hans-Jürgen Kerner|author3=Cheryl Maxson|display-authors=etal|title=The Eurogang Paradox: Street Gangs and Youth Groups in the U.S. and Europe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ccTcBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT166 |year= 2012|publisher= Springer Science|isbn= 978-94-010-0882-2|pages=166–167}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author1=Maurice Crul|author2=Flip Lindo|author3=Ching Lin Pang|title=Culture, Structure and Beyond|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lKHEO7um2nQC |year= 1999|publisher= Het Spinhuis|isbn= 978-90-5589-173-3|pages=66–67}}</ref><ref name=minahan1590>{{cite book|author=James Minahan|title=Encyclopedia of the Stateless Nations: L-R|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=u9Lq_8Ozf5cC |year=2002|publisher=Greenwood Publishing |isbn=978-0-313-32111-5|pages=1590–1592}}</ref>。

由于历史原因，大量里夫人弃用传统的[[里夫语|里夫语]]，而改操[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]或是[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]<ref name=britrif>The Editors of Encyclopædia Britannica, [https://www.britannica.com/topic/Rif-people Rif people], Encyclopaedia Britannica</ref>。里夫人分为不同的部落，不同的部落也有不同的文化和语言传统<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SpiOAwAAQBAJ|title=Tribe and Society in Rural Morocco|last=Hart|first=David M.|publisher=Routledge|year=2014|isbn=9781135302542|pages=105|language=en}}</ref>。1923年，里夫人曾建立[[里夫共和国|里夫共和国]]，抵抗西班牙和法国军队的入侵。
